{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_2","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,220p' .claude/plans/ACTIVE_PLAN.md\"","aggregated_output":"# ACTIVE_PLAN\n\nTrack Status: active\n\n## Milestone Status\n\n- [x] Milestone 1 — Architecture Stabilization\n- [x] Milestone 2 — Board Interaction Quality\n- [x] Milestone 3 — Insight and Guidance Layer\n- [x] Milestone 4 — Operational Reliability\n- [x] Milestone 5 — Publishable Product Quality\n\n## Current Task Plan\n\n- `task-plans/cma-codex-communication-optimization-task-plan.md`\n\n## Current Slice\n\n- [ ] Task 1 review — confirm optimistic queued and failure cues now stay local for `sendPrompt` and `auto-continue`, then decide whether Task 1 can close.\n\n## Next Handoff\n\n- Review Task 1 against the current implementation before opening Task 2; only patch the smallest remaining gap if queued/failure state still depends on a full refresh somewhere.\n- When the communication-optimization track is complete, switch to `task-plans/codex-loop-control-surface-task-plan.md`.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
